CAST
====

Usage: cast <spell> [target]

Cast a spell you have learned. Spells consume mana and require sufficient
skill in the associated magic school.

Examples:
  cast fireball orc     - Cast fireball at an orc
  cast heal             - Cast heal on yourself
  cast magic missile wolf

Requirements:
  - Must know the spell (learned from a guild)
  - Must have enough mana
  - Must meet minimum skill requirement
  - Heavy armor causes spell failure chance

Spell failure from armor:
  None/Robes: 0%    Light: 10%    Medium: 30%    Heavy: 60%

See also: spells, skills, mana
